name: BeautyBayssOrange2.5d
description:
BeautyBayssOrange2.5d

A merge model mixed with Beauty2.5d(0.5weight) and abyssorange 2.5(0.5weight).

And the abyssorange 2.5 mixed with AOM2-Hardcore(0.5weight) and AOM3(0.5weight).

So the whole model actually uses the above three models, if you have, you can merge by yourself.

I choose this model as my works sample model, becauseit has good compatibility with various Lora ,it's convenient for my test work.

I also prepared a fp16 version, please choose your like.
